					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10948911#post-4449625</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10948911/scp-4260#post-4449625</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2019 00:46:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Are you referring to Horowitz as the mortal? Horowitz has, for all intents and purposes, ascended to godhood and merged with Death. As much as Death can be called a person, Horowitz now is; less of a &quot;storing&quot; and more of a succession and rebirth.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
